title: Guy Penrod- Hymns
description:
Chart-busting gospel favorite, Guy Penrod puts his powerhouse sound on timeless hymns. This collection of all-new recordings features twelve beloved hymns, including a duet with the incomparable George Beverly Shea on the song "Does Jesus Care?" This keepsake is for anyone who loves hymns or enjoys the incredible gospel music legacy of Guy Penrod.
